duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide periodontal therapies and other hygiene-related services to improve oral health of patients.
Perform oral hygiene dental treatment and care in accordance with state guidelines.
Conduct patient screening, medical history, and dental charting.
Apply fluoride and protective sealants, remove calculus, stain, and plaque.
Provide nutritional counseling and self-care programs to prevent disease.

education_certification.credential: Active Hygiene license for the state of New Jersey
